<view class="verification-page"><block wx:if="{{isVerified}}"><view class="verified-status"><view class="status-icon">✅</view><text class="status-title">校园认证已通过</text><text class="status-desc">您已完成校园身份认证，可以使用所有功能</text><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['confirmAndBack',['$event']]]]]}}" class="retry-btn" bindtap="__e"><text>确认</text></view></view></block><block wx:else><view class="verification-form"><view class="form-header"><text class="header-icon">🎓</text><text class="header-title">校园身份认证</text><text class="header-desc">请填写真实信息完成身份认证</text></view><view class="form-section"><view class="form-item"><view class="item-label"><text>姓名</text><text class="required">*</text></view><input class="item-input" placeholder="请输入真实姓名" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" maxlength="10" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','name','$event',[]],['formData']]]]]}}" value="{{formData.name}}" bindinput="__e"/><block wx:if="{{errors.name}}"><text class="error-tip">{{errors.name}}</text></block></view><view class="form-item"><view class="item-label"><text>学号</text><text class="required">*</text></view><input class="item-input" placeholder="请输入11位学号" placeholder-class="input-placeholder" type="number" maxlength="11" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','studentId','$event',[]],['formData']]]]]}}" value="{{formData.studentId}}" bindinput="__e"/><text class="hint-tip">学号为11位数字</text><block wx:if="{{errors.studentId}}"><text class="error-tip">{{errors.studentId}}</text></block></view><view class="form-item"><view class="item-label"><text>学院</text><text class="required">*</text></view><picker mode="selector" range="{{allDepartments}}" value="{{departmentIndex}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['onDepartmentChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="{{['picker-input',(formData.department)?'has-value':'']}}"><text class="picker-text">{{formData.department||'请选择学院'}}</text><text class="picker-arrow">▼</text></view></picker><block wx:if="{{errors.department}}"><text class="error-tip">{{errors.department}}</text></block></view></view><view class="notice-section"><view class="notice-title">📌 注意事项</view><view class="notice-item"><text>• 请确保填写的姓名、学号和学院信息真实有效</text></view><view class="notice-item"><text>• 学院信息请谨慎填写，填写后无法修改</text></view><view class="notice-item"><text>• 认证通过后可享受所有功能</text></view></view><button class="{{['submit-btn',(isSubmitting)?'submitting':'']}}" disabled="{{isSubmitting}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['submitVerification',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"><text>{{isSubmitting?'提交中...':'提交认证'}}</text></button></view></block></view>